        "body": "<img width=\"1512\" height=\"856\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/414a9daa-bdf1-4e7e-8164-b260e235e472\" />\n\n<img width=\"1508\" height=\"864\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9c372c64-4052-48d8-9d57-16371b0ed88d\" />\n\nThis PR proposes small, presentation-only improvements to the Draft 2019-09 page to improve readability and visual consistency with newer drafts (e.g., 2020-12). The changes focus on typography, spacing, and Markdown rendering using existing components and styles. No changes are made to navigation, sidebar structure, draft classification, or specification content.\n\nIf this approach looks good, I’d be happy to be assigned to the issue and continue with the work.\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [x] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
